OL,3,CControversial plans to house asylum
OL,4,Cseekers in derelict prison, scrapped
OL,6,FDame Angela Eagle, Home Office
OL,7,FMinister for Border Security and
OL,8,FAsylum, wrote to the MP today (9
OL,9,FDecember) to confirm that the Home
OL,10,FOffice would not progress with this
OL,11,Fsite. Instead, the site would be sold.
OL,13,FBexhill MP, Dr Kieran Mullan, welcomed
OL,14,Fthe news, and said: "I know residents
OL,15,Fwill join me in welcoming the
OL,16,Fgovernment's decision not to proceed
OL,17,Fwith an immigration accommodation site
OL,18,Fat Northeye in Bexhill.
