OL,6,F"I want to thank campaigners, and
OL,7,Fcross-party councillors across all
OL,8,Flayers of local government for
OL,9,Ffighting against this plan.
OL,11,FI've done all I can to support them. I
OL,12,Fam especially pleased for the
OL,13,Fresidents of the Northeye Estate for
OL,14,Fwhom the uncertainty and worry is
OL,15,Fover."
