OL,3,CControversial plans to house asylum
OL,4,Cseekers in derelict prison, scrapped
OL,6,F"It's unfortunate that residents have
OL,7,Ffaced months of uncertainty without
OL,8,Fany information from the previous
OL,9,FGovernment, but I am sure they will,
OL,10,Flike us, be relieved to finally have
OL,11,Fan answer.
OL,13,F"The letter promises that steps will
OL,14,Fbe taken to ensure the onward sale of
OL,15,Fthe site is carried out appropriately
OL,16,Fand we look forward to a discussion
OL,17,Fwith the Home Office regarding the
OL,18,Ffuture use of the site."
